   Ring Status

     This page should update about once every minute. If it doesn't, make
     sure you have JavaScript turned on. If it still fails, you can
     update manually by hitting reload or alt-reload (option-reload on a
     Mac). A text-based status page is also available.

   current ring status

     The Accelerator Status Hotline at (510) 486-6766 (ext. 6766 from Lab
     phones) features a recorded message giving up-to-date information on
     the operational status of the accelerator.

     Live beam-position data is available for insertion devices around
     the ring.

     You can also view the Operations Group's Beam History Archives by
     following text-based links or by submitting a form.


